  "description": "A mod that allows console commands to be executed over the ingame Minecraft chat.",
  "body": "# ConsoleMC\n<a href=\"https://github.com/J-onasJones/ConsoleMC/blob/master/LICENSE\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/J-onasJones/ConsoleMC?style=flat&color=900c3f\" alt=\"License\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/V2EsuUVmWh\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/702180921234817135?color=5865f2&label=Discord&style=flat\" alt=\"Discord\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/consolemc\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/consolemc?logo=modrinth&label=&style=flat&color=242629&labelColor=00AF5C&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/consolemc\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/game-versions/consolemc?logo=modrinth&color=242629&labelColor=00AF5C&logoColor=white\"></a>\n\n<a align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jonasjones.dev/mod-badges/fabric-api.png\" width=\"250px\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jonasjones.dev/mod-badges/support-fabric.png\"  width=\"250px\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jonasjones.dev/mod-badges/support-quilt.png\" width=\"250px\"></a>\n\n\n\n<br>\n\n### About\nThis mod allows You to execute shell commands (system commands) on the server's machine through the minecraft chat. The command requires operator rights.\n\n### Warning\nIf the wrong people have access to this command pass-through your server and Network with all it's connected devices are in danger. Make sure that only people You trust have access to the command.\n\n<img src=\"http://cdn.jonasjones.dev/mod-badges/no-support-forge.png\" width=\"250px\">\n<img src=\"http://cdn.jonasjones.dev/mod-badges/available-modrinth.png\" width=\"250px\">\n\n### Setup\n\n1. Download the correct version of the mod into your mods folder.\n2. Restart your Minecraft server and You're good to go!",
